# No server secrets required.
#
# This app is "bring your own backend": each user enters their Neon connection,
# Azure Speech key, and AI endpoint in the in-app Settings screen, stored in
# their own browser. The Neon connection goes browser-direct (never hits this
# server); Azure & AI calls are proxied for CORS but nothing is stored here.
#
# Just deploy the app (e.g. to Vercel) — no env vars needed.
